milestones.description: Shane Warne and Paul Reiffel's 119-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 50 between Rod Marsh and Rodney Hogg
Shane Warne and Paul Reiffel's 119-run partnership is the highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 117 between Dave Houghton and Iain Butchart
Wessels has broken the record for most catches (23) in ODIs for SA, going past Jonty Rhodes's 22
